misc: Originally known to many Hector players from his past appearances in Finnkampen events
biography: Jari, a golfer hailing from the esteemed Archipelagia Golf Club, is set to make his debut at the Hector Trophée in the upcoming 2025 edition. Though new to this particular tournament, Jari is no stranger to the competitive circuit, having previously participated in Finnkampen events, where he became known to many of the Hector players.

Considered by some to be retired from Hector events, Jari's return to competitive play has been met with excitement. Known for his thoughtful approach to the game and a meticulous attention to detail, Jari is admired for his commitment to the sport. While the Hector Trophée presents a fresh challenge, those familiar with Jari's dedication anticipate a noteworthy performance.
